opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 20th day of August, 2008, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus and the Application for an Immediate Healing are DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
